acter is part of a contiguous sequence representing the ten\ndecimal digits in order from 0 to 9, this function returns the first and\nlast characters from this range.\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Decimal` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L710-L713","name":"Unicode.isDecimal","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isDecimal","doc":"Check if character represents a decimal digit\n\nFor this property, a character must be part of a contiguous sequence\nrepresenting the ten decimal digits in order from 0 to 9.\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Decimal` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L687-L702","name":"Unicode.getDigit?","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getDigit?","doc":"Get value of digit\n\nUnicode properties: `Numeric_Value`, `Numeric_Type=Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L673-L681","name":"Unicode.isDigit","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isDigit","doc":"Check if character represents a digit in base 10\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L653-L662","name":"Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition.loop","kind":"opaque","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition.loop","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L641-L663","name":"Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition","doc":"Get canonical decomposition of character (`NFD`)\n\nUnicode property: `Decomposition_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L629-L632","name":"Unicode.getTitleChar","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getTitleChar","doc":"Map character to titlecase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the titlecase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Titlecase_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L617-L620","name":"Unicode.getUpperChar","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getUpperChar","doc":"Map character to uppercase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the uppercase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Uppercase_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L605-L608","name":"Unicode.getLowerChar","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getLowerChar","doc":"Map character to lowercase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the lowercase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Lowercase_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L590-L590","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isCn","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isCn","doc":"Check if unassigned character (`Cn`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Cn` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/f1c1a2239d9a6ea98469aa3d4d4814d73d4bb286/UnicodeBasic.lean#L584-L587","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isUnassigned","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isUnassigned","doc":"Check if unassigned character (`Cn`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Cn` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/l